<div class="rise-docs-page">
  <div class="docs-hero">
    <h1>PERFIORA THEME DOCUMENTATION</h1>
    <p>A comprehensive guide for merchants to harness the full potential of our luxury design system.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-content">
    <div class="docs-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">1. What's Included</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <div class="doc-card">
          <div class="card-icon">✧</div>
          <h3>Premium Templates</h3>
          <p>Over 10 meticulously designed pages including Homepage, Product Details, Our Story, Sustainability, FAQ, Contact, and more. All engineered for a high-end luxury aesthetic.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-card">
          <div class="card-icon">✦</div>
          <h3>Advanced Animations</h3>
          <p>Integrated GSAP scroll triggers, glassmorphism hover effects, and ambient glow particles that make the store feel alive without compromising performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-card">
          <div class="card-icon">✧</div>
          <h3>Global Design System</h3>
          <p>Centralized CSS variables for colors, typography, and spacing under the "Perfiora" preset, ensuring brand consistency across every pixel of your storefront.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="docs-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">2. How to Use the Theme</h2>
      <div class="instruction-block">
        <h3>Navigating the Shopify Editor</h3>
        <p>The Perfiora theme is fully integrated with Shopify's Online Store 2.0. To start building:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Go to <strong>Online Store > Themes > Customize</strong>.</li>
          <li>Select any page from the top dropdown (e.g., "Pages > about" or "Pages > contact").</li>
          <li>Click on sections in the left sidebar to change headings, upload custom images, and edit text blocks.</li>
          <li>For global changes like primary colors or typography, click the <strong>Theme Settings (gear icon)</strong> on the left panel.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="instruction-block">
        <h3>Best Practices for Imagery</h3>
        <p>To maximize the luxurious feel of Perfiora, we highly recommend:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Using <strong>transparent PNGs</strong> for product shots. This allows the background ambient glow and particles to shine through.</li>
          <li>Utilizing high-resolution, moody, or dark-toned lifestyle photography for banners and collages to seamlessly blend with the dark background.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
